          <title>Vasilevskiy stars as the Lightning stop the Jets' 7-game win streak with a 4-1 victory</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Andrei Vasilevskiy made 24 saves in his 300th NHL win, and the Tampa Bay Lightning stopped Winnipeg’s seven-game win streak with a 4-1 victory over the Jets. Vasilevskiy is the 40th goaltender in league history to win 300 games.]]></description>
